The,Onfido,Background,Checks,API,is,an,application,for,submitting,background,check,requests,This,RESTful,API,uses,standard,HTTP,verbs,with,responses,in,JSON,Calls,to,the,API,are,made,over,HTTPS,and,HTTP,Basic,Auth,is,used,for,authentication,Onfido,offers,checks,for,identity,and,document,verification,right,to,work,criminal,history,and,terrorist,watchlist,searches